(birds chirping)

57:10.890 --> 57:12.990
(chattering)

57:25.370 --> 57:28.540
(toilet flushing)

57:29.710 --> 57:32.180
(footsteps on stairs)

57:33.610 --> 57:35.410
(knocking)

57:35.410 --> 57:37.050
(girl) Mom.

57:38.320 --> 57:39.950
(knocking continues)

57:40.250 --> 57:41.690
Mom!

57:44.590 --> 57:46.960
(clattering)
(grunts) Oh!

57:46.960 --> 57:48.960
(clatters)
(groans)

57:48.960 --> 57:51.030
(man) Try to keep it dry.
